---
import Button from "@/components/input/Button.astro";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Sponsors"
  description="Fand Server 支持入口。"
  keywords={["fand", "minecraft", "support", "sponsor"]}
  canonical="/sponsors"
>
  <header class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 pt-32 pb-20 text-center lg:pt-36">
    <div class="tech-label mb-4">SUPPORT</div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white md:text-6xl">支持 Fand Server</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
      赞助体系还没有正式接入。现在最直接的支持方式，是提交可复现问题、性能样本和代码审查意见。
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
      <Button variant="filled" href="https://github.com/MC20018/Fand" external>前往 GitHub</Button>
    </div>
  </header>
</Layout>
